about your transfer.

1145
01:11:57,284 --> 01:11:58,919
He said there's no problem.

1146
01:12:04,491 --> 01:12:06,493
-Wine?
-Sure.

1147
01:12:08,195 --> 01:12:09,463
[pouring]

1148
01:12:21,074 --> 01:12:22,242
To civilization.

1149
01:12:23,177 --> 01:12:24,578
