the way we were together

1159
01:13:16,630 --> 01:13:17,931
and it's just a lie?

1160
01:13:20,968 --> 01:13:23,904
I mean, maybe it's just my ego,
you know? Maybe I just--

1161
01:13:24,671 --> 01:13:26,306
I just can't admit
that I made a mistake.

1162
01:13:28,408 --> 01:13:30,577
